item.title: Another team with Red Rover?
item.content:encoded:
I've known about this team for a while now, but it doesn't seem to be up….and no one is saying anything so I will.
Red Rover + Pinky + Robogirl = Not A Team Bonus! "They're just an example on the Team page! Okay, FINE. +1 Levels!"
If you don't believe me try it out for yourself, you may need to have them all lvl 1 or not…I'm not sure
